threats.title: Intercepting requests
threats.description: An attacker can intercept client requests, modify data or steal credentials.

threats.title: Resource Exhausting
threats.description: An attacker can send large amount of requests to the server and/or send a special crafted request to exhaust the server resources.
threats.mitigation:
- Apply rate limit
- Auto scale resources

threats.title: Frontend Servlet Directory Listing Disclosure
threats.description: An attacker can list files & folders stored in the Web Servlet.
